1802
02:15:47.942 --> 02:15:51.605
I knew it. I knew it...

1803
02:15:55.683 --> 02:15:59.483
Train, I'm gonna take this kid,
and I'm gonna come back for you.


1804
02:15:59.520 --> 02:16:01.249
I'm gonna come right back for you.

1805
02:16:01.288 --> 02:16:03.153
All right. I'll be right here.

1806
02:16:07.394 --> 02:16:09.521
[in Italian] Liberty!

1807
02:16:21.542 --> 02:16:23.737
I'm gonna come
right back for you.


1808
02:16:28.549 --> 02:16:29.777
Damn!

1809
02:16:43.163 --> 02:16:44.357
[man, in German] Forward!

1810
02:16:55.309 --> 02:16:56.333
Train.

1811
02:17:09.623 --> 02:17:11.318
