1824
02:18:25.566 --> 02:18:27.727
[yelling in German]

1825
02:18:46.987 --> 02:18:50.081
- [in Italian] Go! Go! Go!
- Run! Run!


1826
02:18:51.225 --> 02:18:52.351
Stamps!

1827
02:18:52.393 --> 02:18:53.690
Stamps!

1828
02:18:53.727 --> 02:18:55.092
Stamps!

1829
02:18:56.663 --> 02:18:58.494
- [gun fires]
- [screams]


1830
02:19:00.901 --> 02:19:02.368
Get down!

