1833
02:19:05.873 --> 02:19:07.636
[screaming]

1834
02:19:21.021 --> 02:19:22.818
- [gun firing]
- [man screaming]


1835
02:19:39.840 --> 02:19:41.330
Stamps!

1836
02:20:10.804 --> 02:20:11.964
[in Italian] Angelo.

1837
02:20:12.005 --> 02:20:13.973
Angelo.

1838
02:20:14.007 --> 02:20:15.531
You're not dead anymore.

1839
02:20:15.576 --> 02:20:17.976
Open your eyes.

1840
02:20:18.011 --> 02:20:19.342
Angelo.

1841
02:20:23.317 --> 02:20:25.751
Arturo, where am I?

1842
02:20:25.786 --> 02:20:27.083
It's not important.

1843
02:20:27.120 --> 02:20:29.111
We have to go.

1844
02:20:29.156 --> 02:20:30.783
Am I going to Heaven?

1845
02:20:30.824 --> 02:20:32.553
No, you're going home.

1846
02:20:32.593 --> 02:20:33.685
Where's my home?

1847
02:20:33.727 --> 02:20:35.592
Angelo, I'll show you.

1848
02:20:35.629 --> 02:20:36.960
Who's there?

1849
02:20:36.997 --> 02:20:39.397
Your Papa. Remember him?

1850
02:20:40.767 --> 02:20:42.132
What about my friend...

1851
02:20:42.169 --> 02:20:44.000
the Chocolate Giant?

1852
02:21:00.354 --> 02:21:01.878
You have to remember him,

1853
02:21:02.723 --> 02:21:04.213
me,

1854
02:21:04.258 --> 02:21:06.192
all of this.

1855
02:21:06.226 --> 02:21:08.694
