- Right here.


1866
02:23:16.123 --> 02:23:17.613
Guys, we need a hand.

1867
02:23:22.629 --> 02:23:25.063
Stand by. Lift!

1868
02:23:37.310 --> 02:23:40.143
[man] Easy, y'all. Real easy.

1869
02:23:40.180 --> 02:23:44.344
It's gonna be OK, Hector. You're going
back home to New York, man.


1870
02:23:52.759 --> 02:23:55.023
[man 2] Reconnaissance photos
were accurate.


1871
02:23:55.062 --> 02:23:58.122
General Almond wouldn't listen.
Go get those dog tags.


1872
02:23:58.165 --> 02:23:59.462
[man 3] Yes, sir.

1873
02:23:59.499 --> 02:24:01.694
[man 2] I need a full report,
