1874
02:24:03.236 --> 02:24:05.796
- [man 3] "Stamps, Aubrey."
- [man 4] Got it.


1875
02:24:07.808 --> 02:24:10.504
- [man 3] "Cummings, Bishop."
- [man 4] Check.


1876
02:24:13.580 --> 02:24:16.048
- [man 3] "Train, Samuel."
- [man 4] Got it.


1877
02:24:23.457 --> 02:24:26.551
Well done, corporal.
You earned yourself a Purple Heart.


1878
02:24:26.593 --> 02:24:29.027
- Get this man to the aid station.
- Yes, sir!


1879
02:24:29.062 --> 02:24:30.586
Detail.

1880
02:24:38.371 --> 02:24:41.306
[Tim] Come on, Mr. Negron.
You're clean as a board of health.


1881
02:24:41.341 --> 02:24:46.870
You got no kids, no debts. No enemies.
