1882
02:24:46.913 --> 02:24:52.044
Why stick a German Luger in a guy's
chest three months short of retirement?


1883
02:24:53.253 --> 02:24:55.585
You're looking at 25 to life, pal.

1884
02:25:08.301 --> 02:25:10.929
<i>[woman] State v. 
Hector Negron.</i>

1885
02:25:10.971 --> 02:25:16.375
Case 14, dockets 79A and 34B.

1886
02:25:16.409 --> 02:25:20.539
Judge Trinkoff presiding. All rise.

1887
02:25:22.516 --> 02:25:27.249
Peter Hammond, District Attorney,
representing People, State of New York.


1888
02:25:27.287 --> 02:25:30.279
Michael Decker, legal aid for defense.

1889
02:25:31.224 --> 02:25:33.249
It's Zana Wilder.

1890
02:25:33.293 --> 02:25:35.591
Michael, let me handle this.

1891
02:25:35.629 --> 02:25:39.998
